OL,3,CWork progressing on memorial site two
OL,4,Cyears on from Jersey explosion
OL,6,FPlans for a memorial to remember the
OL,7,Fpeople who lost their lives following
OL,8,Fthe Haut du Mont explosion in Jersey
OL,9,Fare progressing.
OL,11,FTen islanders died at the Haut du Mont
OL,12,Fflats in St Helier two years ago on
OL,13,FSaturday 10 December 2022.
OL,15,FTributes were laid at the temporary
OL,16,Fmemorial near the scene this morning
OL,17,F(Tuesday 10 December 2024), but new
OL,18,Fproposals are expected to be published
OL,19,Fearly next year.
