OL,3,CWork progressing on memorial site two
OL,4,Cyears on from Jersey explosion
OL,6,FProposals shaped by the victims'
OL,7,Frelatives are expected to include a
OL,8,Fseated area of reflection on the Pier
OL,9,FRoad site.
OL,11,FAndium Homes is also looking to
OL,12,Frefurbish the residential blocks that
OL,13,Fsurvived the impact and will be giving
OL,14,Fdisplaced residents the option to
OL,15,Freturn if they wish.
OL,17,FIn September last year, three housing
OL,18,Fblocks were demolished following a
OL,19,Frecommendation from the Recovery
OL,20,FCoordination Group and Andium Homes.
