OL,3,CWork progressing on memorial site two
OL,4,Cyears on from Jersey explosion
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Jersey's Attorney General
OL,7,Fis continuing to consider charges
OL,8,Ffollowing the investigation by States
OL,9,Fof Jersey Police and the Health and
OL,10,FSafety Inspectorate into the cause of
OL,11,Fthe blast.
OL,13,FThree suspects were originally
OL,14,Farrested in August of last year.
OL,16,FThe investigation is one of the
OL,17,Fbiggest in Jersey Police's history and
OL,18,Fhas involved 2,078 lines of enquiry,
OL,19,F8,412 documents, 1,173 statements and
OL,20,F2,001 exhibits.
