OL,3,CWork progressing on memorial site two
OL,4,Cyears on from Jersey explosion
OL,6,FRelatives and displaced residents are
OL,7,Fnext due to meet in January, where
OL,8,Fthey will once again be consulted on
OL,9,Fplans for the site's future.
OL,11,FThe 10 people who died were 72-year-
OL,12,Fold Peter Bowler, Raymie Brown (71),
OL,13,FRomeu and Louise De Almeida (67 and 64
OL,14,Fyears), Derek and Sylvia Ellis (61 and
OL,15,F73 years), Ken and Jane Ralph (72 and
OL,16,F71 years), 63-year-old Billy Marsden
OL,17,Fand 73-year-old Kathleen 'Kathy'
OL,18,FMcGinness.
